title: Zack Williams’ CV
text:
Student, Computer Scientist.

Click Here



2021 - Present Brigham Young Unversity Idaho.
2014 - 2018 Trinity College, Cambridge



May 2024 - Present AI Contractor, Outlier.ai (Online)

Task assignments
Ai improvements

November 2022 - December 2022 Student Consultant, Small Business Management, BYU_I (Rexburg, Idaho)
Member of student team that consulted with Tacos El Guey, a small taco truck business operating out of Twin Falls. Owner needed an idea of when she could step away from her business. - Created a Pro Forma based on past financial information that can be adjusted to give the owner an idea of what is needed financially for her to step away. - Preformed an analysis on future labor cost they will endure. - Made applicable recommendations pertaining to her current operations
January 2021 - April 2021 Warehouse Associate, PetWish (Buford, Georgia)

Packed and labeled merchandise to prepare for loading and shipment to customers.
Picked and prepared numerous daily shipments in controlled atmosphere warehouse environment.
Moved boxes, containers and pallets with special-purpose equipment to meet demanding production targets.
Organized warehouse design to maximize space for stock while allowing for high volume traffic zones.

Febuary 2018 - December 2018 Warehouse Associate, Lowe’s Home Improvment (Suwanee, Georgia)

Built and maintained relationships with peers and upper management to drive team success.
Assisted teammates with sales-processing tasks to meet daily sales goals.
